highlights.text: “ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 975 days straight.
YOUNGOHM has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “เจิดจรัส” is the highest at #6.
“สถานีดวงจันทร์” by Whatcharawalee is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 101 spots at #75.
“Remind” by Moderndog is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #199.
